<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,1341,1438]" pageId="5" pageNumber="435">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,276,1341,1365]" pageId="5" pageNumber="435">FIGURE 4.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Jocqué &amp; Jocque &amp; Mbende, 2022" authorityName="Jocqué &amp; Jocque &amp; Mbende" authorityYear="2022" box="[283,485,1341,1365]" class="Arachnida" family="Telemidae" genus="Cangoderces" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="435" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="wewef" status="sp. n.">
<emphasis box="[283,485,1341,1365]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="435">Cangoderces wewef</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[493,550,1341,1365]" pageId="5" pageNumber="435">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[493,550,1341,1365]" pageId="5" pageNumber="435" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
A–B: Paratype male (247535); C–D: Paratype female (247534). A. Male palp, retrolateral view. B. do.; slightly tilted towards frontal view; C. Endogyne, ventral view. D. Spinnerets and colulus, ventral view. Scale lines: 100 μm. E: Embolus; PTA: Prolateral Tubular Apophysis; ST: Spermatheca.
</paragraph>
